title: what an AI said
pid: 891b1912-54aa-483b-8053-93c22a2494d9
body: |2-
  Ficción Sonora: The modern term used by major networks (like RTVE in Spain) for high-budget, immersive audio dramas.
  Radioteatro
  Radionovela: Traditionally more "soap opera" style
  Podcast de Ficción: The term you'll most often find on Spotify or Apple Podcasts.
